{"tid":461581,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"天晉再破頂！將軍澳兩房戶二手價955萬成交","createTime":"2017-11-07T17:24:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-09T08:02:52.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"987055112d8c6f7dea6f0c7fc0fe50553a9c9560","tid":461581,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T17:24:10.000Z","msg":"11月07日(二) 14:16   <br />\n<br />\n利嘉閣梁敬嚴稱，將軍澳天晉1期3座中層E室，實用面積538方呎，成交價955萬港元，創全區兩房戶二手價新高，實用呎價約17,751元。據了解，原業主2011年以約479.5萬元購入，持貨近6年帳面賺475.5萬元，單位升值近1倍。同屋苑對上兩房戶成交紀錄約945萬元。"},{"pid":"a1a70599e6f381b0632dee75095a984dc036d4e9","tid":461581,"uid":2155,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T17:34:40.000Z","msg":"唔明天晉有咩咁好<br />\n利申住將軍澳"},{"pid":"590a18014a5fa1582ffce1d48f35587831b5c13c","tid":461581,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T11:04:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28995781df32799a36222098105255988694d502","tid":461581,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T14:53:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b591c1f3f89d724e46e96c3b97f3baa9f9d1db9","tid":461581,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T15:03:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔明天晉有咩咁好<br />\n利申住將軍澳</blockquote><br />\n新地樓<br />\n將軍澳黎講戶型好炒"},{"pid":"f6c85a40214f0291ace042624a1b75717466f904","tid":461581,"uid":33483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T15:04:18.000Z","msg":"將軍澳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f80b4e71ab916dc2309ee7b750ef5741cd27d91","tid":461581,"uid":143940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T17:14:22.000Z","msg":"仲係好平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a126b5b14e6ce5a4b5171532bc5e4eec0f1b0e1c","tid":461581,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"